  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA68">
<l>pārtta kaṭuvaṉ cuṉainīr niḻaṟkaṇṭu</l>
<l>pērttōr kaṭuvaṉeṉap pērntu – kārtta</l>
<l>kaḷaṅkaṉikkuk kainīṭṭum vēṅkaṭamē mēṉāḷ</l>
<l>viḷaṅkaṉikkuk kaṉṟeṟintāṉ veṟpu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Vēṅkaṭam , where the peering monkey sees [its own] reflection in the water</l>
<l>of the mountain pool, moves on in the thought ‘another monkey’ [and]</l>
<l>extends [its] hand for the blackened Kaḷam fruits, is the mountain of him</l> 
<l>who, on a former day, threw the calf for the fruits of the woodapple tree.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
